item.title: Clean Traffic No Default SCS Trailers V1.6 1.56 ETS2
item.description:
Euro Truck Simulator 2 Mods | American Truck Simulator Mods | October 2, 2025

Clean Traffic No Default SCS Trailers V1.6 1.56 ETS2

Tired of those repetitive SCS default trailers cluttering the roads?
Clean Traffic – No Default SCS Trailers is a lightweight but powerful mod for Euro Truck Simulator 2, designed to strip out all SCS-made trailers from traffic — giving way to custom trailer packs and a more immersive driving experience.

Removes Almost all default SCS trailers from AI traffic
Ideal for use with custom AI trailer mods like Real Company Packs
Improves realism, aesthetics, and traffic variety
Clean, optimized for performance
Compatible With All Trailer Packs Mods

Perfect for realism lovers, mod collectors, and anyone wanting cleaner, custom-only roads.

Installation:
Place the .scs file into your ETS2 mod folder
Activate it in your mod manager and BELOW other trailer mods
Hit the road and enjoy the new look of clean logistics!

Credits: Kass

How to install ETS2 mods or ATS Mods
In Euro Truck Simulator 2 it’s easy to install mods. You just need to download mod from here, copy/unzip files into: “My Documents\Euro Truck Simulator 2\mod” folder or if you play ATS please install mods to: “My Documents\American Truck Simulator\mod” folder. To unzip files you can use: WinRAR or 7zip. After that you need to activate the mods you want to use.
Report bugs in the comments and help modders improve this mod. Always check the comments, you can find a solution.

DOWNLOAD MOD

item.description:
Euro Truck Simulator 2 Mods | American Truck Simulator Mods | October 2, 2025

Titan Trucker No Damage Invincibility V1.5 1.56 ETS2

Key Features:
Compatible ATS 1.56.x
Complete damage immunity for truck, trailer, and cargo
No penalties for collisions, rough driving, or over-speeding
Engine, tire, and chassis invincibility—never visit a service station again
Compatible with Quick Jobs, Freight Market, and World of Trucks contracts
Works alongside physics mods, weather mods, and traffic packs

Why Use Titan Trucker?
Explore freely without worrying about repair bills
Take risky shortcuts or drive off-road
Great for beginner players learning to handle big rigs
Ideal for YouTubers, streamers, and mod reviewers and for testing

Installation:
Download and unzip the mod file winrar or 7zip
Move the .scs file into your Documents/Euro Truck Simulator/mod folder
Activate in Mod Manager and place it near the top of the load order
